GNOME 3's GUI is a total upheaval for users of GNOME 2. Getting familiar with it, at least for its basics, is a matter of minutes provided the user is directed to the right entry point. A rather good entry point to quickly get familiar with this new GUI is the [https://help.gnome.org/users/gnome-help/stable/index.html.en GNOME Help] page.

